\c 41
\s Munyengetero pakurwara
\d Kumutungamiriri wekuimba. Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Wakaropafadzwa anorangarira murombo; Jehovha achamununura nezuva rechakaipa.
\v 2 Jehovha achamuchengetedza, nekumuraramisa; achava wakaropafadzwa panyika; uye hamungamukumikidzi kuchido chevavengi vake.
\v 3 Jehovha achamutsigira panhovo yeurwere; muchashandura nhovo yake yose pahosha yake.
\p
\v 4 Ini ndakati: Jehovha, ndinzwirei tsitsi; poresai mweya wangu; nokuti ndakakutadzirai.
\v 5 Vavengi vangu vanotaura kuipa pamusoro pangu \add vachiti\add*: Uchafa rinhi, zita rake rirove?
\v 6 Kunyange kana achiuya kuona, anotaura zvisina maturo; moyo wake unozviunganidzira uipi; anobuda panze, ndokutaura.
\v 7 Vese vanondivenga vanoita zeve-zeve pamwe chete kundirwisa; vanondirongera zvakaipa kwandiri; \add vachiti\add*:
\v 8 Chinhu chakaipa chakanamatira paari; uye sezvo akarara pasi, haachamukizve.
\v 9 Hongu, murume weushamwari hwangu wandaivimba maari, aidya chingwa changu, wakandisimudzira chichitsinho.
\p
\v 10 Asi imwi, Jehovha, ndinzwirei tsitsi, mugondisimudzira, kuti ndivatsive.
\v 11 Neizvi ndinoziva kuti munofadzwa neni, nokuti muvengi wangu haana kufara pamusoro pangu.
\v 12 Kana ndiri ini, munonditsigira pauchokwadi hwangu; uye munondiisa pamberi penyu kusvika rinhi narinhi.
\p
\v 13 Ngaarumbidzwe Jehovha, Mwari waIsraeri, kubva pakusingaperi kusvika pakusingaperi. Ameni, uye Ameni.